          <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/9192/9192029.png" alt="Speed" />
          <h5 class="fw-semibold">Lightning Fast</h5>
          <p class="text-muted">Built for performance. Instant redirection, no delays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
